<h1>Accessibility statement: Orange Digital Accessibility Guidelines Web Site</h1>

<div class="summary">
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-lg-12">
            <h2 class="h4 mt-4">Context</h2>
            <p>Orange SA undertakes to make its internet, intranet, extranet websites and its mobile
                applications accessible in accordance with article 47 of Law No. 2005-102 of February 11, 2005.</p>
            <p>To this end, it implements the following strategy and actions:</p>
            <p><a href="https://oran.ge/accessibility-plan"
                    title="the Digital Accessibility Multi-year Plan 2024 - 2026 (PDF, 165Ko)">the Digital Accessibility
                    Multi-year Plan 2024 - 2026 (PDF, 165Ko)</a>.</p>
            <p>This accessibility statement applies to https://a11y-guidelines.orange.com/en/.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
